  "texts": [
    "On the same line, Zheng et al. (2018) devised an algorithm for early AD diagnosis through PET scans utilizing an ensemble of AlexNets (EnAlexNets).",
    "The EnAl-exNets algorithm effectively addresses the limited information provided by a single image mode and simplifies the requirements for multi-mode images in the diagnosis process.",
    "The suggested method is divided into four main steps: (i) anatomical volume identification, (ii) enhancement of data, (iii) classification of patches, and (iv) discriminating different types of dementia.",
    "It attains an accuracy of 91%.",
    "Compared to utilizing multi-modal images, this approach is more robust in capturing distinguishing features and demonstrates superior performance."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "On the same line, Zheng et al. (2018) devised an algorithm for early AD diagnosis through PET scans utilizing an ensemble of AlexNets (EnAlexNets)."
  ]
